name: VYPOR REZ #14
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. VYPOR Rez was the first of the hatchlings to crawl from the pit. This is his young form, and although small, he is extremely fast and deadly. 

By holding a character in this series you are eligible for secret airdrops. Collect and hold all of the characters for the chance to receive the comic when it is available. Copyright @smileghostnf
